    • 方法详细资料

      • check

        private void check()
            throws java.io.IOException
        This method used the Javalin to organise the command, it will send the command end with "/md51/compare/md52", the server will return a string with the information about the simple difference and the Levenshtein-distance.

        The md51 and md52 refers to the md5 codes of the files. If the user type the path or the content directly it will invoke the Read in method to get the md5 code.It will print error massage if the files doesn't exist in the database.

        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - throws when the client can' connect to the server correctly.

      • Compareout

        public void Compareout(javafx.scene.control.SplitPane pane)
                throws java.io.IOException
        参数:
        pane - The method will use the left side of the splitpane to build the interface for compare.
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - When can't connect to the server correctly.
